Fannie Mae
v.
Price 257P16-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 8, 2016

Mr. William Gerald Price, Pro Se.

Ms. Natasha M. Barone, Attorney at Law, For Federal National Mortgage Association a/k/a Fannie Mae.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th of September 2016 by Petitioner for Certified Certificate of Registration pursuant to F.A.R.A., USC 22 § 611 :
